# Performance Budgets

## Frontend
- Core SDK: < 8 KB gzipped. Full with widget: < 25 KB. With React: < 35 KB.
- No main thread blocking > 16ms. Measure bundle size in CI.

## Backend (p95)
- Event ingestion: < 20ms. Classification: < 50ms. Cached hints: < 5ms. Haiku: < 300ms. Spatial: < 1s. Dashboard: < 200ms.
- No DB query > 100ms. EXPLAIN ANALYZE on new queries.
- WebSocket establishment: < 100ms. Handle 10k concurrent connections per instance.

## Monitoring
- Track p50/p95/p99. Track bundle size trends. Alert on regressions.
